  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category</strong>: Clan<br /><strong>Prerequisite</strong>: Fujou Clan, 8+<br /><strong>Description</strong>: You awake one of the clan's most rare techniques, the ability to see beyond your eyes. You gain the following:</p><ul><li><p>While your <strong>Tatarigan</strong> is active, you can choose one point within 200 feet of you as an action to activate <strong>Overlooking View</strong>. You become able to see as if standing in that point. While <strong>Overlooking View</strong> is active, you are blinded from your surroundings unless they can be seen from this point. You can return to your normal view as a bonus action.</p></li><li><p>While using <strong>Overlooking View</strong>, Genjutsu you cast that do not require NT components originate from the Point of View of <strong>Overlooking View</strong>.</p></li><li><p>While using <strong>Overlooking View</strong>, genjutsu you cast that do not require NT components and require an attack roll ignore half cover and three-quarter cover.</p></li></ul>",
